startAt.description: The index of the first item to return in a page of results (page offset).

maxResults.description: The maximum number of items to return per page.

id.description: The list of issue security scheme IDs. To include multiple issue security scheme IDs, separate IDs with an ampersand: `id=10000&id=10001`.

projectId.description: The list of project IDs. To include multiple project IDs, separate IDs with an ampersand: `projectId=10000&projectId=10001`.
